Dependencies:

  * Recent Django (tested on 1.2.3)

  * Recent ``reversion`` middleware (``easy_install django-reversion``;
    currently using 1.3.2)
  
After a clean install, 

  * Copy ``local_settings.py.dist`` to ``local_settings.py`` and customize
    (details in file -- don't neglect to set the SECRET_KEY). 
    
  * Run ``python manage.py syncdb`` and add superuser when prompted.

